comments.body: Needles CA borders AZ and NV so maybe those species should be considered also? Regardless, a siting of a horned lizard in this area has been very rare for me at least
Only 4 species of "Horned Lizards" have been IDed on iNat for California: https://www.inaturalist.org/observations?place_id=14&taxon_id=36299

results.description: Honey toad! Rare siting in this area
